    "requirementText": "The CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index (RH) for the candidate centrifugal blood pump shall not exceed 1.4 across all five evaluated flow-speed operating combinations. Predictions exceeding RH = 1.4 shall be deemed non-compliant and require design modification prior to regulatory submission.",
